{
  "stem": "25809.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember the big bang-- the big-- big band sounds of the Beethoven's-- what is it-- 'Unfinished'?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then the sound of [INAUDIBLE] is Radio Vrij Nederland, Radio Free Netherlands, Radio Oranje, and listened to the reports.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And yeah, we had maps on the wall, trying to keep track of where the Allies were and, of course, besides ourselves when finally we were liberated by the-- mostly by the Canadian-- Canadians.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To a degree I remember it, because I went into Utrecht.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- everybody went into Utrecht to-- because we knew that the Canadians were coming in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was a marvelous, unbelievable experience [LAUGHS] to see those cars coming  in, yeah.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- so they-- I don't know, it was just a beautiful experience to be free again and walk around and do what you wanted to do.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyhow, we went into-- I remember going into Utrecht a couple of times.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then my father said, well, I'm going back to Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he and--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, well they came over to the-- they came over to the farmhouse and said, well-- my father, he was a funny guy in a way.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's easy to-- to talk him down because of the many unpleasant things that he did and the unpleasant experience we had.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "On the other hand, I have to keep in mind that he was under tremendous pressure.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He felt very guilty that his mother, sister, and his cousin were hauled away by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That-- that-- that really tore at him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it may have been one of the things why he was so incredibly moody in his way.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he had really suffered from that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But anyhow, one day my father said, OK, we are going to Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, yeah, I said.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
